# Design tokens

Single source of truth for color, spacing, typography, radius, motion, and elevation values used across the product.

## Where tokens live

- **Authoritative source:** {{path_to_tokens_file_—_e.g._src/styles/tokens.css_/_tokens/tokens.json_/_Figma_variables}}
- **Build pipeline:** {{how_tokens_flow_from_source_to_runtime_CSS_/_JS_—_or_"direct_import"}}
- **Refresh cadence:** {{every_design_review_/_release-locked_/_...}}

## Token categories

- **Color** — see [`../styles/color.md`](../styles/color.md) for scales + usage rules
- **Typography** — see [`../styles/typography.md`](../styles/typography.md)
- **Spacing** — see [`../styles/spacing.md`](../styles/spacing.md)
- **Radius** — see [`../styles/elevation.md`](../styles/elevation.md) or a dedicated radius file
- **Motion** — see motion rubric in `docs/rubrics/motion-design.md`

## Rules

- **Never use raw hex / rgb / px values in components** — always reference a token
- **Token additions go through** {{PR_review_/_RFC_/_design_crit}} — not ad-hoc
- **Deprecate instead of delete** — mark tokens removed with `@deprecated` comment for at least one release before removing

## Tokens index

Machine-readable: [`../index-manifest.json`](../index-manifest.json) (populated by build or by hand).
